lead_paragraph: Unheralded Swede Rikard Karlberg shot a first round eight-under-par 64 to outshine a stellar field at the WGC-HSBC Champions on Thursday, finishing a shot ahead of Rickie Fowler at a wet Sheshan International Golf Club.

headline.print_headline: Karlberg Outshines Stellar Field for Shanghai Lead
